sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Express Server
    participant PP as Passport.js
    participant OIDC as Replit OIDC Provider
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over U,DB: Login Flow

    U->>FE: Click "Sign In"
    FE->>API: GET /api/login
    API->>PP: passport.authenticate("replitauth")
    PP->>OIDC: Redirect to authorization endpoint
    OIDC->>U: Show login page (Google/GitHub/Apple/Email)
    U->>OIDC: Enter credentials
    OIDC->>API: Redirect to /api/callback with auth code
    API->>PP: passport.authenticate("replitauth")
    PP->>OIDC: Exchange code for tokens
    OIDC-->>PP: {access_token, refresh_token, id_token}
    PP->>PP: Extract user claims from tokens
    PP->>DB: UPSERT user record
    DB-->>PP: User record
    PP->>DB: CREATE session
    DB-->>PP: Session ID
    PP-->>API: Set session cookie
    API->>FE: Redirect to / (302)
    FE->>API: GET /api/auth/user
    API-->>FE: User profile JSON
    FE->>U: Show authenticated dashboard

    Note over U,DB: Token Refresh Flow

    FE->>API: GET /api/auth/user (expired token)
    API->>PP: isAuthenticated middleware
    PP->>PP: Check token expiry
    PP->>OIDC: refreshTokenGrant(refresh_token)
    OIDC-->>PP: New tokens
    PP->>PP: Update session with new tokens
    PP-->>API: next()
    API-->>FE: User profile JSON

    Note over U,DB: Logout Flow

    U->>FE: Click "Logout"
    FE->>API: GET /api/logout
    API->>PP: req.logout()
    PP->>DB: DELETE session
    API->>OIDC: buildEndSessionUrl
    OIDC-->>U: Redirect to home page
